Package: englishfootball
Type: Package
Title: A Comprehensive Database on the Premier League and the English Football League (1888-2022)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Joshua C.",
           family = "Fjelstul",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "joshfjelstul@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9494-260X"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: This package contains the Fjelstul English Football Database. The database covers every match ever played in the top four tiers of English football, including every match in the Premier League and the English Football League from the inaugural season of the Football League in 1888 through the end of the 2021-22 season. The database includes datasets, which cover seasons, teams, matches, team appearances (one observation per team per match), and end-of-the-season standings (league tables). 
Date: 2022-07-10
